日日禅

禅修,打坐,静坐,日记,佛教,道教,灵修,内观,禅坐,禅,日日禅,禅宗,修行,快乐
Zen,Meditation,Diary,Journal,Buddhism,Taoism,ZenPath,Cultivation,Chan,Insight,Vipassana,Spirit

https://twitter.com/zenpathapp



禅修日记本，记录您每日的禅修心得。
坚持每日规律地禅修，必将获得身与心的利益。

功能介绍：
- 适合禅修者的闹钟，轻轻‘叮’一声后（敲钵声），便自行停止，不会重复，您不用再立即移动身体去关闭闹钟，更方便禅修者平缓地延长打坐时间。
- 根据闹钟设定，自动记录禅坐的开始与结束时间。便于禅修者自我监督，养成每日禅修的良好习惯。
- 每次禅修后，都可以记下禅修时的感受体会，以便今后自己进行省察，或者导师进行辅导。

使用说明：
- 长按闹钟时间数字，可以修改闹钟的时长。
- 建议每次打坐前，调至【飞行模式】，切断网络，以免受到电话，短信，各种提醒的惊扰。本应用可以在网络恢复时，手动同步保存禅修记录。
- 请不要调至【勿扰模式】或者【静音模式】，那样您就听不到下座的铃声了。

Zen Path, a meditation journal, record your everyday meditation learnings.
Regularly meditate can benefit both your mental and physical health.

Features:
- Alarm designed for meditator, just a subtle tibetan bell sound, no repeat, no need to move your body to switch off alarm, more convenient to smoothly extend your meditation.
- Automatically record start/end time for your meditation, for self review and self motivation, build up your good habit.
- Write down your own feeling and learning every time after meditate, really helpful for self retrospection or tutor instruction in the future.

Instructions:
- Long tap alarm numbers, enable alarm time modification.
- Please turn on [Airplane mode] every time before meditation, cut off network, avoid phone ring, message, notification disturbing. ZenPath could upload your record after network back to normal.
- Please not turn on [Do not disturb] or [Silent] mode, otherwise you won't able to notify by the alarm.
